-- Yahoo Japan: to buy back up to $305 million own shares
-- 
-- Tue Mar 17, 2009 3:12am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/17/businesspro-us-yahoo-japan-buyback-idUSTRE52G15G20090317

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - Yahoo Japan Corp ( 4689.T ) said it would buy back up to 1.185 million of its own shares, worth up to 30 billion yen ($305 million), before the market opens on Wednesday and then cancel them. 

 That will be equivalent to 2 percent of its shares outstanding. (Reporting by Sachi Izumi)